/-- Full-carry stopped-tree 22.1A data for one Appendix N shell.

This is the manuscript-shaped input when the Lemma 22.1 stopped-tree Chernoff
budget has already been built on the whole carry skeleton.  The shell-paid
multiplier and the final finite layer-cake area smallness estimate remain
